===message:Of course the least expensive (monetarily speaking, not culturally or historically), is to let nature take its course.  Society has enough forewarning to save the important works of art and historical records.  Television crews and photographers can document the sinking of Venice.  Then when technology catches up, we can celebrate with The Raising of Venice.  Until then, Italy can boast a new dive destination.
